query:
SELECT 
  c.name as category,
  COUNT(DISTINCT p.id) as product_count,
  p.imageUrl as sample_image_url
FROM products p
LEFT JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
LEFT JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id
WHERE pc.isPrimary = 1
GROUP BY c.name, p.imageUrl
ORDER BY c.name, COUNT(p.id) DESC
LIMIT 30;
